 "Science fiction writers need great imagination to visualize future technologies.", "chinese": "科幻作家需要丰富的想象力来想象未来的科技.", "highlights": [{"text": "imagination", "color": "#FFD93D"}], "images": [{"url": "https://images.pexels.com/photos/3931342/pexels-photo-3931342.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940", "alt": "A thoughtful male writer typing on a vintage typewriter, surrounded by crumpled papers.", "position": "center", "size": "medium"}], "englishAudioUrl": "/audio/tts/example_en_scene_005_be0fc6.wav", "englishAudioDuration": 6.0}, "narration": "Science fiction writers need great imagination to visualize future technologies. 意思是:科幻作家需要丰富的想象力来想象未来的科技.", "narrationLang": "zh", "durationSeconds": 18, "audioUrl": "/audio/tts/narration_scene_005_363744.wav", "audioDuration": 11.3}, {"id": "scene_006", "type": "summary", "content": {"type": "summary", "points": ["imagination是名词,意思是想象力、想象或创造力", "词根imag-来源于拉丁语,表示形象、图像,引申为想象", "后缀-ation表示行为过程,imagination即想象的过程和结果", "相关词汇包括image(形象)、imagine(想象)、imaginative(富有想象力的)"]}, "narration": "今天我们学习了imagination这个单词.它由词根imag-(形象)和后缀-ation(行为过程)组成,意思是想象力或想象.记住这个词根,我们可以联想记忆更多相关词汇.希望大家课后多加练习,熟练掌握这个高频词汇！", "narrationLang": "zh", "durationSeconds": 23, "audioUrl": "/audio/tts/narration_scene_006_29243f.wav", "audioDuration": 20.2}]}, "audioUrls": {"scene_001_narration": "C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace-english\\skills\\avatar-vocab-video-generator\\scripts\\public\\audio\\tts\\narration_scene_001_8c78b5.wav", "scene_002_narration": "C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace-english\\skills\\avatar-vocab-video-generator\\scripts\\public\\audio\\tts\\narration_scene_002_4585f4.wav", "scene_003_narration": "C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace-english\\skills\\avatar-vocab-video-generator\\scripts\\public\\audio\\tts\\narration_scene_003_bec860.wav", "scene_003_root_imag-": "C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace-english\\skills\\avatar-vocab-video-generator\\scripts\\public\\audio\\tts\\root_imag-_cf5